author: ekoneil
msg: Significant low-level work in the NetUI expression language.  This change contains a bunch of performance enhancements that should decrease the amount of memory consumed by each parsed expression by 30-50%.  It also includes a bunch of internal API cleanup which is okay because the o.a.b.n.script.el package isn't part of the public API.
Also adds a bunch of Javadoc to the internal APIs.
